title: SEND_DUI_MOUSE_DOWN
content:
0x5D01F191// SendDuiMouseDown
void SEND_DUI_MOUSE_DOWN(long duiObject, char* button);Parameters:duiObject: The DUI browser handle.button: Either 'left', 'middle' or 'right'.Injects a 'mouse down' event for a DUI object. Coordinates are expected to be set using SEND_DUI_MOUSE_MOVE.
